                                    <tr><td><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%"><tbody><tr><td style="" align="left" valign="top"></td></tr><tr><td style="" align="left" valign="top"></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td></td></tr><tr><td></td></tr><tr><td><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" data-editable="image" data-mobile-width="1" style="" width="100%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="left" style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(29, 29, 29);" class="tdBlock"><a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=A4&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=t&" target="_blank"><img src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1502.png?img1434255097001" width="620" data-origsrc="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1489.png" data-src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1502.png|620|73|600|42|0|0|1" alt="Bryan Johnson is an entrepreneur and investor. He is the founder of OS Fund and Braintree, the latter of which was bought by eBay in 2013 for $800 million in cash." data-createnew="true" style="border: 0px none transparent; display: block; width: 100%; max-width: 100% !important;"></a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" data-editable="text"><tbody><tr><td align="left" valign="top" style="padding: 20px 30px 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(100, 175, 27);"><div style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=Aw&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=c&" target="_blank" title=""><font size="22" style="font-size: 22px; color: rgb(100, 175, 27); font-weight: bold;">The Rags to Riches Philosopher: </font><span style="color: rgb(100, 175, 27); font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; background-color: inherit;">Bryan Johnson’s Path to $800 Million</span></a></div><div style=""><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#262626;font-size:14px"></span></div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" data-editable="image" data-mobile-width="1" style="max-width: 100% !important;" width="99%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="center" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; display: inline-block;" class="tdBlock"><a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=Ad&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=L&" target="_blank"><img src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1504.png?img1434255097001" width="593" data-src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1504.png|593|474|593|473|0|0|1" data-origsrc="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1503.png" data-createnew="true" style="border: 0px none transparent; display: block; width: 100%; max-width: 100% !important;"></a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0px 30px;"><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" width="100%" data-editable="line"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="center" style="padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px;"><div style="height: 1px; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="" width="1" height="1" style="display:block;"></div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr></tr><tr></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" data-editable="text"><tbody><tr><td align="left" valign="top" style="padding: 5px 20px 20px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); font-style: italic;"><font size="14" style="font-size: 14px; font-style: normal;"><a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=Ae&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=6&" target="_blank" title="" style="font-weight: bold;">Bryan Johnson</a> is an entrepreneur and investor. He is the founder of <a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=Ab&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=F&" target="_blank" title="">OS Fund</a> and <a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=A1&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=v&" target="_blank" title="">Braintree</a>, the latter of which was bought by eBay in 2013 for $800 million in cash.<br><br>Bryan launched OS Fund in 2014 with $100 million of his personal capital to support inventors and scientists who aim to benefit humanity by rewriting the operating systems of life. In other words: he fuels real-world mad scientists.<br><br>His investments include endeavors to cure age-related diseases and radically extend healthy human life to 100+ (<a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=At&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=m&" target="_blank" title="">Human Longevity</a>), replicate the human visual cortex using artificial intelligence (<a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=Ac&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=O&" target="_blank" title="">Vicarious</a>), mine an asteroid (<a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=AL&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=a&" target="_blank" title="">Planetary Resources</a>), reinvent transportation using autonomous vehicles (Matternet), and reimagine food using biology (Hampton Creek), among others.<br><br>Our conversation includes his rags to riches story, his philosophical hardwiring, negotiating/sales tactics, and even parenting. We cover a ton of ground with a fascinating and deep mind.<br><br>Enjoy!</font></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" data-editable="image" data-mobile-width="1" width="41%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="left" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; display: inline-block;" class="tdBlock"><a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=A6&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=I&" target="_blank"><img src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1510.jpg?img1434255097001" width="244" data-src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1510.jpg|244|85|223|76|-1|0|1" height="85" data-origsrc="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1493.jpg" alt="The Tim Ferriss Show" style="border: 0px none transparent; display: block;"></a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" data-editable="image" data-mobile-width="1" width="41%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="left" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; display: inline-block;" class="tdBlock"><a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=AF&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=i&" target="_blank"><img src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1511.jpg?img1434255097001" width="244" height="85" data-src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1511.jpg|244|85|223|76|0|0|1" data-origsrc="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1495.jpg" alt="The Tim Ferriss Show" style="border: 0px none transparent; display: block;"></a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" data-editable="image" data-mobile-width="1" style="" width="91%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="center" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; display: inline-block;" class="tdBlock"><a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=Av&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=P&" target="_blank"><img src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1506.png?img1434255097001" width="545" data-src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1506.png|545|56|545|54|0|0|1" data-origsrc="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1505.png" style="border: 0px none transparent; display: block; width: 100%; max-width: 100% !important;"></a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" data-editable="text"><tbody><tr><td align="left" valign="top" style="padding: 15px 20px 10px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); font-style: italic;"><div style=""><font size="14" style="font-size: 14px; font-style: normal;"><ul><li><span style="background-color: inherit;">Listen to this episode <a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=A6&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=I&" target="_blank" title="">on iTunes</a>.</span></li><li><span style="background-color: inherit;">Stream by <a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=Av&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=P&" target="_blank" title="">clicking here</a>.</span></li><li><span style="background-color: inherit;">Download as an MP3 by <a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=Av&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=P&" target="_blank" title="">right-clicking here and choosing “save as”</a>.</span></li></ul><div style=""><br></div><div style=""><span style="font-weight: bold;">Do you enjoy listening to world-class entrepreneurs?</span>  If so, you might enjoy my conversations with Peter Thiel. He co-founded PayPal in 1998, which was sold to eBay for $1.5 billion. He was also the first outside investor in Facebook (!) and has since created another billion-dollar+ startup called Palantir. Stream our conversation below or <a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=Am&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=7&" target="_blank" title="">right-click here</a> to download:</div></font></div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" data-editable="image" data-mobile-width="1" style="" width="91%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="center" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; display: inline-block;" class="tdBlock"><a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=Am&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=7&" target="_blank"><img src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1509.png?img1434255097001" width="545" data-src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1509.png|545|55|545|55|0|0|1" data-origsrc="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1507.png" style="border: 0px none transparent; display: block; width: 100%; max-width: 100% !important;"></a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" data-editable="image" data-mobile-width="1" width="48%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="center" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; display: inline-block;" class="tdBlock"><a href="http://www.fourhournewsletter.com/click.html?x=a62e&lc=AO&mc=e&s=bihEd&u=w&y=o&" target="_blank"><img src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1513.png?img1434255097001" width="288" data-src="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1513.png|288|134|288|134|0|0|1" height="134" data-origsrc="http://multimedia.fourhournewsletter.com/4hourweek/1/1/photos/1512.png" style="border: 0px none transparent; display: block;"></a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0px;"><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" width="100%" data-editable="line"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="center" style="padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px;"><div style="height: 1px; line-height: 1px; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="" width="1" height="1" style="display:block;"></div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" data-editable="text"><tbody><tr><td align="left" valign="top" style="padding: 15px 20px 10px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); font-style: normal;"><div style=""><font size="14" style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-